column5: EUR/USD could rise as much as 5% if a Ukraine ceasefire is agreed followed by the resumption of gas supplies A potential ceasefire between Russia and Ukraine seems more likely. Trump and Russian President Vladimir Putin reportedly agreed to start negotiating an end to the war in Ukraine.

column2: EUR/USD trades below 1.0500 after pausing winning streak
column5: EUR/USD halts its four-day winning streak, hovering around 1.0490 during Asian trading hours. Liquidity during the North American session may remain thin as all major US financial markets will be closed on Monday for the federal holiday, Presidents' Day.
